ely predicted. Then, the robust control of the line-of-sight is tackled\nas a $\\mathcal H_{\\infty}$ problem that allows to reach the performance\nobjectives in terms of disturbance rejection, control bandwidth and actuators\nlimitations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Dec 2021 11:36:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-21"}
