near bias parameter $b_{\\mathrm{NL}}$. We use our\nmodelling to assess the ability of Stage-IV surveys to constrain primordial\nnon-Gaussianity. Finally, we show how this non-linear bias parameter can\neffectively renormalize diverging relativistic contributions at large scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Dec 2021 15:15:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-21"}
